  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you chose this Divotion Way, you get a reserve of Healing Dice (d6) equal to your level. As an action you can touch a creature and spend one of these d6 to heal it by an amount of hit points equal to the result of that dice roll + your Wisdom modifier.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You can also remove a poison, a disease or a curse when treating someone in this way.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Starting at 5th level, you can spend two dice with a single touch, at 11th level three and at 17th level up to four dice.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">If you have no Healing Dice left to spend, you can use the target’s hit dice.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">You can recover all spent Healing Dice only after taking a long rest.</span> </p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
